-- raw sql results do not include filled-in values for 'event.created_date'


SELECT
    (DATE(event.CREATED_AT )) AS `event.created_date`,
    COUNT(DISTINCT `group`.id) AS `group.count`,
    COUNT(DISTINCT model_set.id) AS `model_set.count`
FROM event
LEFT JOIN user  AS user ON event.user_id = user.id
LEFT JOIN user_facts_role ON user.id = user_facts_role.user_id
LEFT JOIN role ON user_facts_role.role_id = role.id
LEFT JOIN model_set ON role.model_set_id = model_set.id
LEFT JOIN group_user ON user.id = group_user.user_id
LEFT JOIN  `group`   AS `group` ON `group`.id = group_user.group_id
GROUP BY
    1
ORDER BY
    (DATE(event.CREATED_AT )) DESC
LIMIT 25
